# outfitter-dev

Internal Claude Code plugin for Outfitter.dev development.

## Installation

```bash
/plugin install ./outfitter-dev
```

## Structure

```
./
├── .claude-plugin/
│   └── plugin.json
├── skills/
├── agents/
├── commands/
├── hooks/
├── .claude/
│   └── rules/
└── scripts/
```
